{
  "text": "By means of the PTA procedure, we were able to successfully treat the renal artery stenosis in the 2 patients with moyamoya disease who had renovascular hypertension. Thus, we were able to control the hypertension in the 2 patients with moyamoya disease. We believe that the PTA procedure is the first choice of treatment for renal artery stenosis in patients with moyamoya disease. In previous reports, [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] 15 renal artery stenosis in moyamoya disease has been treated with renal autotransplantation or PTA.",
